    About this hotel

    Set on 20 hectares of gardens, this upscale resort with Berber touches is 5 km from both the Jemaa el-Fnaa marketplace and the Koutoubia Mosque and 8 km from Majorelle Garden.

    Check-in time: 3:00 PM
    Check-out time: 12:00 PM

    We visited this beautiful hotel twice this month - both times to have lunch. On both occasions we were given a very warm welcome and were impressed by the fabulous setting and design of the pool and grounds, giving a very relaxing and zen-like feel. Our experience at the pool restaurant was made extra special by Mousaabe, who was not only friendly and warm, but also very professional and attentive - we felt like old friends when we returned a week later! Also, whilst enjoying the pool, Oussama looked after us so well, making sure we were comfortable and had everything we needed, always with a smile. Above all the team who work here make this hotel a superior experience - we will definitely be back when we visit Marrakech (three times a year) and look forward to our return! Thank you.

    Annakhil

    The sprawling suburb of Annakhil includes golf courses and palm groves, with paths and horse-carriage tours through 100,000 trees at El Palmeral. Inside that park is Musée de la Palmeraie, showing a century of Moroccan paintings in a 1940s colonial farmhouse. MACAAL is a more modern space, displaying pan-African art. Residential areas have casual tagine restaurants, while resort hotels have chic bars and bistros.

    About this hotel

    Set on 20 hectares of gardens, this upscale resort with Berber touches is 5 km from both the Jemaa el-Fnaa marketplace and the Koutoubia Mosque and 8 km from Majorelle Garden. …

    Luxe 1-and 2-bedroom suites have free Wi-Fi, hammams and Nespresso machines; some add private plunge pools, outdoor dining areas and/or terraces. Posh villas offer courtyards and gardens.

    Free perks consist of breakfast and airport transfers. There are elegant Moroccan and Chinese restaurants, as well as a casual eatery with international fare. Other amenities include an outdoor pool, bike rentals, and a fitness center offering personal trainers and yoga classes.
